Frontend: Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
Backend: FastAPI (Python) + Pydantic for schemas
Queue: Celery + Redis (simpler to start) or BullMQ (Node-based)
Database: PostgreSQL (for user data, jobs) + Prisma/SQLAlchemy
AI: Gemini 2.5-Flash (structured output) 
Storage: Local for dev, AWS S3/Linode Object Storage for prod
Deployment: Github Pages + Render for API security
